# Loose source-photo drops in the repo root (processed 800x800 copies live in
# images/people/). Keeps `git add -A` from sweeping them into commits.
/*.png
!/favicon-16.png
!/favicon-32.png
!/favicon-48.png
!/og-card.png
!/icon-512.png
!/apple-touch-icon.png
/*.jpg
/*.jpeg
/*.heic
/*.HEIC
/*.JPG
/*.stl
.DS_Store
